<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr" xmlns:th="http://www.thymeleaf.org">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
		<title>Bibliothèque Municipale - Découvrez notre collection</title>
		<style>:root
		{
			--primary: #8E4A49;
			--secondary: #A67C52;
			--light: #f9f9f9;
			--dark: #3a3a3a;
			--accent: #E0C9A6;
			--background: #f5f2e9;

			/* Variables pour la section Books */
			--primary-color: #8E4A49;
			--secondary-color: #f5f2e9;
			--accent-color: #A67C52;
			--border-color: #dee2e6;
		}

		* {
			margin: 0;
			padding: 0;
			box-sizing: border-box;
			font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
		}

		body {
			background: var(--background);
			color: var(--dark);
			min-height: 100vh;
			line-height: 1.6;
		}

		.header {
			background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5), rgba(166, 124, 82, 0.7)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507842217343-583bb7270b66?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1920&q=80') center/cover no-repeat;
			height: 75vh;
			display: flex;
			flex-direction: column;
			justify-content: flex-start;
			align-items: center;
			text-align: center;
			color: white;
			position: relative;
			overflow: hidden;
			padding-top: 12rem;
		}

		.nav {
			position: absolute;
			top: 0;
			left: 0;
			width: 100%;
			display: flex;
			justify-content: space-between;
			align-items: center;
			padding: 1.8rem 3rem;
			z-index: 10;
			background: rgba(58, 58, 58, 0.2);
			backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
		}

		.logo {
			font-size: 1.8rem;
			font-weight: 700;
			color: white;
			text-decoration: none;
		}

		.logo span {
			color: var(--accent);
		}

		.nav-links {
			display: flex;
			gap: 2rem;
		}

		.nav-links a {
			color: white;
			text-decoration: none;
			font-weight: 500;
			transition: all 0.3s ease;
			position: relative;
		}

		.nav-links a:hover {
			color: var(--accent);
		}

		.nav-links a::after {
			content: '';
			position: absolute;
			width: 0;
			height: 2px;
			bottom: -5px;
			left: 0;
			background-color: var(--accent);
			transition: width 0.3s ease;
		}

		.nav-links a:hover::after {
			width: 100%;
		}

		.cta-buttons {
			display: flex;
			gap: 1rem;
		}

		.cart-icon {
			position: relative;
			margin-right: 1.5rem;
			cursor: pointer;
			color: white;
			font-size: 1.3rem;
		}

		.cart-badge {
			position: absolute;
			top: -8px;
			right: -8px;
			background: var(--primary);
			color: white;
			font-size: 0.7rem;
			width: 18px;
			height: 18px;
			border-radius: 50%;
			display: flex;
			align-items: center;
			justify-content: center;
		}
		.user-dropdown {
			position: relative;
			cursor: pointer;
			margin-right: 15px;
		}

		.user-name {
			color: white;
			font-weight: 500;
			display: flex;
			align-items: center;
			gap: 5px;
		}

		.dropdown-menu {
			position: absolute;
			top: 100%;
			right: 0;
			background: white;
			border-radius: 8px;
			box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
			width: 180px;
			opacity: 0;
			visibility: hidden;
			transform: translateY(10px);
			transition: all 0.3s ease;
			z-index: 100;
			margin-top: 10px;
		}

		.user-dropdown:hover .dropdown-menu {
			opacity: 1;
			visibility: visible;
			transform: translateY(0);
		}

		.dropdown-menu a {
			display: flex;
			align-items: center;
			padding: 12px 15px;
			color: var(--dark);
			text-decoration: none;
			transition: all 0.2s ease;
			border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
		}

		.dropdown-menu a:last-child {
			border-bottom: none;
		}

		.dropdown-menu a:hover {
			background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
			color: var(--primary);
		}

		.dropdown-menu i {
			margin-right: 10px;
			font-size: 0.9rem;
		}

		.btn {
			padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
			border-radius: 30px;
			text-decoration: none;
			font-weight: 600;
			transition: all 0.3s ease;
			border: none;
			cursor: pointer;
		}

		.btn-primary {
			background: var(--primary);
			color: white;
			box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(142, 74, 73, 0.4);
		}

		.btn-primary:hover {
			background: #a85958;
			transform: translateY(-3px);
			box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(142, 74, 73, 0.6);
		}

		.btn-outline {
			background: transparent;
			color: white;
			border: 2px solid white;
		}

		.btn-outline:hover {
			background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
			transform: translateY(-3px);
		}

		.hero-content {
			max-width: 800px;
			padding: 0 2rem;
			z-index: 2;
			display: flex;
			flex-direction: column;
			align-items: center;
		}

		.hero-content h1 {
			font-size: 3.5rem;
			margin-bottom: 1rem;
			font-weight: 700;
		}

		.hero-content p {
			font-size: 1.2rem;
			margin-bottom: 2rem;
		}

		.center-buttons {
			display: flex;
			gap: 1rem;
			justify-content: center;
			margin-top: 2rem;
		}

		.search-container {
			position: absolute;
			top: 15%;
			left: 50%;
			transform: translateX(-50%);
			display: flex;
			width: 80%;
			max-width: 600px;
			border-radius: 50px;
			overflow: hidden;
			box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
			z-index: 5;
		}

		.search-input {
			flex-grow: 1;
			padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
			border: none;
			outline: none;
			font-size: 1rem;
		}

		.search-btn {
			background: var(--primary);
			color: white;
			padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
			border: none;
			cursor: pointer;
		}

		.features {
			padding: 5rem 10%;
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
			gap: 3rem;
		}

		.feature-card {
			background: white;
			border-radius: 20px;
			padding: 2rem;
			box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
			transition: all 0.3s ease;
			text-align: center;
		}

		.feature-card:hover {
			transform: translateY(-10px);
			box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
		}

		.feature-icon {
			width: 80px;
			height: 80px;
			display: flex;
			align-items: center;
			justify-content: center;
			margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
			border-radius: 50%;
			font-size: 2rem;
			color: var(--primary);
			background: rgba(142, 74, 73, 0.1);
			border: 2px dashed rgba(142, 74, 73, 0.3);
		}

		.feature-card h3 {
			margin-bottom: 1rem;
			font-size: 1.5rem;
		}

		/* ===== STYLES AMÉLIORÉS POUR LA SECTION BOOKS ===== */
		.books {
			padding: 5rem 10%;
			background: var(--secondary-color, #f8f9fa);
			animation: slideInUp 0.5s ease-out;
		}

		.section-title {
			text-align: center;
			margin-bottom: 3rem;
			position: relative;
		}

		.section-title h2 {
			font-size: 2.5rem;
			display: inline-block;
			color: var(--primary-color, #2c3e50);
			font-weight: 700;
			position: relative;
			padding-bottom: 0.75rem;
		}

		.section-title h2::after {
			content: '';
			position: absolute;
			width: 100px;
			height: 4px;
			background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary-color, #2c3e50), var(--accent-color, #e67e22));
			bottom: -10px;
			left: 50%;
			transform: translateX(-50%);
			border-radius: 2px;
		}

		.book-grid {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
			gap: 1.5rem;
			margin-top: 2rem;
		}

		.book-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color, #dee2e6);
    position: relative;
    height: 100%;
}
		.book-card::before {
			content: '';
			position: absolute;
			top: 0;
			left: 0;
			width: 5px;
			height: 100%;
			background-color: var(--primary-color, #2c3e50);
			opacity: 0.7;
		}

		.book-card:hover {
			transform: translateY(-5px);
			box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
		}

		.book-image {
			height: 300px;
			background-size: contain;
			background-position: center;
			background-repeat: no-repeat;
			padding: 10px;
		}
		.book-card:hover .book-image {
			transform: scale(1.02);
		}
.book-content {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    flex-grow: 1;
    justify-content: space-between;
}


		.book-category {
			color: var(--accent-color, #e67e22);
			font-weight: 600;
			font-size: 0.9rem;
			margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		}

		.book-title {
			font-size: 1.25rem;
			margin: 0.5rem 0;
			color: var(--primary-color, #2c3e50);
			font-weight: 600;
			line-height: 1.4;
		}

		.book-info {
			display: flex;
			justify-content: space-between;
			margin-bottom: 1rem;
			color: #666;
			font-size: 0.9rem;
			flex-wrap: wrap;
			gap: 0.5rem;
		}

		.book-info span {
			display: inline-flex;
			align-items: center;
			gap: 0.3rem;
		}

		.book-info span i {
			color: var(--accent-color, #e67e22);
		}

		.book-price {
			font-weight: 700;
			font-size: 1.2rem;
			color: var(--primary-color, #2c3e50);
			margin-bottom: 1rem;
		}

		.btn-add-to-cart {
			display: inline-flex;
			align-items: center;
			justify-content: center;
			padding: 0.85rem 1.75rem;
			border-radius: 8px;
			font-weight: 600;
			text-decoration: none;
			transition: all 0.3s ease;
			border: none;
			cursor: pointer;
			box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
			font-size: 1rem;
			background-color: var(--accent-color, #e67e22);
			color: white !important;
			width: 100%;
			margin-top: auto;
		}

		.btn-add-to-cart:hover {
			background-color: #d35400;
			transform: translateY(-3px);
			box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
		}

		.btn-secondary {
			display: inline-flex;
			align-items: center;
			justify-content: center;
			padding: 0.85rem 1.75rem;
			border-radius: 8px;
			font-weight: 600;
			text-decoration: none;
			transition: all 0.3s ease;
			border: none;
			cursor: not-allowed;
			box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
			font-size: 1rem;
			background-color: #aaa;
			color: white;
			width: 100%;
			opacity: 0.7;
		}
        




		.btn-action {
			display: inline-flex;
			align-items: center;
			justify-content: center;
			padding: 0.85rem 1.75rem;
			border-radius: 8px;
			font-weight: 600;
			text-decoration: none;
			transition: all 0.3s ease;
			border: none;
			cursor: pointer;
			box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
			font-size: 1rem;
			width: 100%;
			margin-top: auto;
		}

		.btn-emprunter {
            
			background-color: var(--primary);
			color: white !important;
		}

		.btn-emprunter:hover {
			background-color: #a85958;
			transform: translateY(-3px);
			box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
		}

		.btn-emprunter i {
			margin-right: 8px;
		}
		.no-books {
			grid-column: 1 / -1;
			background-color: var(--light-grey, #f1f1f1);
			border-radius: 8px;
			padding: 3rem;
			text-align: center;
			color: #666;
			font-size: 1.2rem;
		}

		/* Animation pour la section Books */
		@keyframes slideInUp {
			from {
				transform: translateY(30px);
				opacity: 0;
			}
			to {
				transform: translateY(0);
				opacity: 1;
			}
		}

		/* Responsive pour la section Books */
		@media(max-width: 992px) {
			.book-grid {
				grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(240px, 1fr));
			}
		}

		@media(max-width: 768px) {
			.books {
				padding: 3rem 5%;
			}

			.section-title h2 {
				font-size: 2rem;
			}

			.book-grid {
				grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(220px, 1fr));
			}
		}

		@media(max-width: 576px) {
			.book-grid {
				grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			}

			.book-info {
				flex-direction: column;
				align-items: flex-start;
			}
		}
		/* ===== FIN DES STYLES AMÉLIORÉS POUR LA SECTION BOOKS ===== */

		.cta-section {
			background: linear-gradient(rgba(142, 74, 73, 0.8), rgba(166, 124, 82, 0.9)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1481627834876-b7833e8f5570?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1920&q=80') center/cover no-repeat;
			padding: 5rem 2rem;
			text-align: center;
			color: white;
		}

		.cta-section h2 {
			font-size: 2.5rem;
			margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		}

		.cta-section p {
			max-width: 600px;
			margin: 0 auto 2rem;
			font-size: 1.1rem;
		}

		.testimonials {
			padding: 5rem 10%;
			text-align: center;
		}

		.testimonial-grid {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(350px, 1fr));
			gap: 2rem;
			max-width: 1200px;
			margin: 0 auto;
		}

		.testimonial-card {
			background: white;
			border-radius: 15px;
			padding: 2rem;
			box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
		}

		.testimonial-text {
			font-style: italic;
			margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
			position: relative;
		}

		.testimonial-text::before {
			content: '\201C';
			font-size: 4rem;
			position: absolute;
			left: -1rem;
			top: -2rem;
			color: rgba(142, 74, 73, 0.2);
		}

		.testimonial-author {
			display: flex;
			align-items: center;
		}

		.author-avatar {
			width: 50px;
			height: 50px;
			border-radius: 50%;
			margin-right: 1rem;
			background-size: cover;
			background-position: center;
		}

		.author-info h4 {
			margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
		}

		.author-info p {
			color: #6c757d;
			font-size: 0.9rem;
		}

		.footer {
			background: var(--dark);
			color: white;
			padding: 4rem 10% 2rem;
			background-image: linear-gradient(to right, #3a3a3a, #4a4a4a, #5a5a5a);
		}

		.footer-content {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
			gap: 3rem;
			margin-bottom: 3rem;
		}

		.footer-column h3 {
			margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
			font-size: 1.3rem;
			position: relative;
			padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
		}

		.footer-column h3::after {
			content: '';
			position: absolute;
			width: 40px;
			height: 3px;
			background: var(--secondary);
			bottom: 0;
			left: 0;
		}

		.footer-column p {
			margin-bottom: 1rem;
		}

		.footer-links {
			list-style: none;
		}

		.footer-links li {
			margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
		}

		.footer-links a {
			color: #b0b0b0;
			text-decoration: none;
			transition: all 0.3s ease;
		}

		.footer-links a:hover {
			color: var(--secondary);
			padding-left: 5px;
		}

		.social-links {
			display: flex;
			gap: 1rem;
		}

		.social-links a {
			width: 40px;
			height: 40px;
			border-radius: 50%;
			background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
			color: white;
			display: flex;
			align-items: center;
			justify-content: center;
			transition: all 0.3s ease;
		}

		.social-links a:hover {
			background: var(--secondary);
			transform: translateY(-3px);
		}

		.footer-bottom {
			border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
			padding-top: 2rem;
			text-align: center;
			color: #b0b0b0;
			font-size: 0.9rem;
		}

		/* Toast notifications pour les ajouts au panier */
		.toast {
			position: fixed;
			bottom: 30px;
			right: 30px;
			display: flex;
			align-items: center;
			background: white;
			border-radius: 8px;
			box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
			overflow: hidden;
			margin-top: 10px;
			opacity: 0;
			transform: translateY(20px);
			transition: all 0.3s ease;
			z-index: 100;
			padding: 0 15px;
		}

		.toast-success {
			border-left: 5px solid #4CAF50;
		}

		.toast-error {
			border-left: 5px solid #F44336;
		}

		.toast-icon {
			padding: 15px 0;
			margin-right: 15px;
			font-size: 1.2rem;
		}

		.toast-success .toast-icon {
			color: #4CAF50;
		}

		.toast-error .toast-icon {
			color: #F44336;
		}

		.toast-message {
			padding: 15px 15px 15px 0;
			font-weight: 500;
		}

		/* Responsive styles */
		@media(max-width: 992px) {
			.hero-content h1 {
				font-size: 2.8rem;
			}

			.search-container {
				top: 5rem;
			}
		}

		@media(max-width: 768px) {
			.nav {
				padding: 1rem 2rem;
			}

			.hero-content h1 {
				font-size: 2.2rem;
			}

			.nav-links {
				display: none;
			}

			.header {
				height: 60vh;
			}

			.search-container {
				top: 4rem;
				width: 90%;
			}
		}
	</style>
</head>
<body>
	
	<!-- Header Section -->
	<header class="header">
		<nav class="nav">
			<a href="#" class="logo">Biblio<span>thèque</span>
				<i class="fas fa-book" style="font-size: 0.9rem;"></i>
			</a>

			<div class="nav-links">
				<a href="#">Accueil</a>
				<a href="/auteur">Auteurs</a>
				<a href="/genre">Genres</a>
			</div>

			<div class="cta-buttons">

				{% if app.user %}
					<div class="user-dropdown">
						<span class="user-name">{{ app.user.nom }}
							<i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
						</span>
						<div class="dropdown-menu">
							<a href="/account">
								<i class="fas fa-user"></i>
								Mon compte</a>
							<a href="{{ path('app_logout') }}">
								<i class="fas fa-sign-out-alt"></i>
								Déconnexion</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				{% else %}
					<a href="/login" class="btn btn-outline">Connexion</a>
					<a href="/register" class="btn btn-primary">Inscription</a>
				{% endif %}
			</div>
		</nav>


		<div class="hero-content">
			<h1>Découvrez notre collection de livres</h1>
			<p>Romans, Essais, BD, Jeunesse - Enrichissez votre bibliothèque personnelle et achetez facilement</p>
			<div class="center-buttons">
				<a href="/livres" class="btn btn-primary">Explorer le catalogue</a>
				<a href="/about" class="btn btn-outline">En savoir plus</a>
			</div>
